OL,3,C'I get my strength from Brianna'
OL,4,CEsther Ghey wants her book to give hope
OL,6,F"In all honesty it was the most
OL,7,Fdifficult thing I have ever done, I
OL,8,Fstripped it right back to when I was
OL,9,Fyounger and to my mental health issues
OL,10,Fand trauma and then what happened to
OL,11,FBrianna, it was really really
OL,12,Fdifficult, but if it helps just one
OL,13,Fperson then it was completely worth it"
OL,15,FEsther wants her book to create a
OL,16,Flasting legacy for Brianna.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
