OL,3,C'I get my strength from Brianna'
OL,4,CEsther Ghey wants her book to give hope
OL,6,FShe said: "I wanted to be able to
OL,7,Fempower people and to give people hope
OL,8,Fas well because what Brianna went
OL,9,Fthrough with her phone she wasn't
OL,10,Falone and with her mental health
OL,11,Fissues she wasn't alone, there are so
OL,12,Fmany young people that are struggling
OL,13,Fnow and so many parents struggling and
OL,14,Fat a loss as to what to do with their
OL,15,Fyoung people"
OL,17,FEsther has taken her campaign to the
OL,18,FHouse of Commons and is now at the
OL,19,Fcentre of the debate around banning
OL,20,Fphones in schools.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
