OL,3,C'I get my strength from Brianna'
OL,4,CEsther Ghey wants her book to give hope
OL,6,FShe has called for smartphones to be
OL,7,Fmade available for under-16s without
OL,8,Fsocial media apps and is campaigning
OL,9,Ffor searches for inappropriate
OL,10,Fmaterial to be flagged to parents.
OL,12,FShe said: "We need to keep young
OL,13,Fpeople off social media, like what
OL,14,FBrianna was accessing online which was
OL,15,Fself harm sites and eating disorder
OL,16,Fsites, that is just the tip of the
OL,17,Ficeberg and I really think we need to
OL,18,Ffollow Australia and ban under 16's
OL,19,Ffrom social media"
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
