OL,3,C'I get my strength from Brianna'
OL,4,CEsther Ghey wants her book to give hope
OL,6,F"There are days when I want to curl up
OL,7,Finto a ball and hide from the world,
OL,8,Fthere are so many people who've been
OL,9,Fthrough similar situations and they
OL,10,Fare campaigning and doing great work
OL,11,Fand when you have this insight you
OL,12,Fknow that something needs to change, I
OL,13,Fget my strength from Brianna and I
OL,14,Fdon't want other people to go through
OL,15,Fwhat she went through"
